name: Brandon Ramirez
description: To pay homage to the often overlooked lionhearts within the web3 community— the devs— we are introducing Web3 Wizards; an ongoing series of on-chain NFT web3 dev characterisations; spotlighting new devs every issue, all designed and minted in-house by DIGITALAX. For this edition we are attributing those that set the standards for defining DeCo as we experience it today and for the future. The DeCo Definers.
